      <altformavail id="aspace_c5298ea364561ce6433dde3203b3d662">
         <head>Existence and Location of Copies</head>
         <p>Golf scrapbooks are available on microfilm (560 frames on 1 reel, 35mm.) from Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library, at cost. Order no. HM184.</p>
      </altformavail>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_4c93970d0593a6f6b63dae11190854da">
